<chapter><title>Reference</title>

<sect1><title>Introduction</title>
<para>
  This section aims to provide a reference for the functionality of the <command>GDMS</command>. 
  The main functionality of this package is provided through the menus. These are of a standard form
  and also include a tear-off feature for flexibility.
</para>
</sect1>

